  "response": "As of October 2023, the smartphone market is dynamic, and the best camera smartphone under 20k INR can vary based on individual preferences and the latest releases. However, here are some of the top contenders in this price range you can consider:\n\n1. **Redmi Note 12 Pro**: Known for its good camera performance, the Redmi Note series often includes well-balanced devices with strong camera capabilities, decent processors, and large batteries.\n\n2. **Realme 9 Pro+**: Realme's offerings have been impressive in terms of camera quality, often combining high-resolution sensors with advanced AI features.\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M32**: Samsung's M series phones often come with solid cameras and good display quality, making them great for photography enthusiasts.\n\n4. **Poco X4 Pro**: The Poco series from Xiaomi has been known for offering strong performance and camera capabilities at competitive prices.\n\n5. **Moto G60**: Motorola's G series has been making waves for good camera systems, often packing high MP counts and versatile lens setups.\n\nRemember, camera performance involves hardware and software optimization, so factors like image processing capabilities also play a crucial role. Always check recent reviews and comparisons for the most up-to-date information, as new models are regularly released.",
